{#
  src/reporting/templates/exposure_report.md.j2
  TraceBurn Exposure Report — Jinja2 Markdown template

  Required variables:
    profile_name    (str)  — Display name of the scanned profile, e.g. "John Smith"
    scan_date       (str)  — Formatted scan timestamp, e.g. "2026-04-01 09:14:32 UTC"
    scan_id         (str)  — UUID string identifying this scan
    scan_type       (str)  — "full" | "spot_check" | "reverification"
    stats           (dict) — Aggregate scan statistics:
                               brokers_checked    (int)
                               exposures_found    (int)
                               previously_removed (int)
                               reappeared         (int)
                               duration_seconds   (int)
                               risk_level         (str): "HIGH" | "MEDIUM" | "LOW" | "CLEAR"
    brokers         (list) — List of broker findings (only brokers with exposures):
                             Each item:
                               name              (str)
                               domain            (str)
                               removal_tier      (int): 1 | 2 | 3
                               region            (str)
                               reappearance_note (str | None)
                               exposure:
                                 status             (str): "found" | "reappeared" | etc.
                                 first_seen         (str)
                                 last_seen          (str)
                                 confidence_score   (float): 0.0–1.0
                                 recommended_action (str)
                                 data_fields        (list):
                                   field_name  (str)
                                   match_type  (str): "exact" | "partial" | "fuzzy"
                                   confidence  (float)
    brokers_clear   (list[str]) — Broker names with no exposure found
    removal_summary (dict) — { submitted, confirmed, pending, failed } (int each)
    breaches        (list) — Optional breach database results:
                             Each: { source (str), breach_date (str), fields_exposed (list[str]) }
    version         (str)  — TraceBurn version string, e.g. "0.1.0"

  Sample rendered output:
    # TraceBurn Exposure Report

    **Generated:** 2026-04-01 09:14:32 UTC
    **Scan ID:** a3f8c1d2-7e45-4b21-9f0a-123456789abc
    **Scan Type:** full

    ---

    ## Profile Summary

    | Field                        | Value         |
    |------------------------------|---------------|
    | Name                         | John Smith    |
    | Brokers Checked              | 87            |
    | Exposures Found              | 14            |
    | Exposures Previously Removed | 3             |
    | Reappearances Detected       | 1             |
    | Scan Duration                | 312s          |

    **Overall Risk Level:** HIGH

    ---

    ## Findings by Broker

    ### Spokeo (spokeo.com)
    ...
#}
# TraceBurn Exposure Report

**Generated:** {{ scan_date }}
**Scan ID:** {{ scan_id }}
**Scan Type:** {{ scan_type }}

---

## Profile Summary

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Name | {{ profile_name }} |
| Brokers Checked | {{ stats.brokers_checked }} |
| Exposures Found | {{ stats.exposures_found }} |
| Exposures Previously Removed | {{ stats.previously_removed }} |
| Reappearances Detected | {{ stats.reappeared }} |
| Scan Duration | {{ stats.duration_seconds }}s |

**Overall Risk Level:** {{ stats.risk_level }}

---

## Findings by Broker

{% if brokers %}
{% for finding in brokers %}
### {{ finding.name }} ({{ finding.domain }})

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| Status | {{ finding.exposure.status }} |
| First Seen | {{ finding.exposure.first_seen }} |
| Last Seen | {{ finding.exposure.last_seen }} |
| Confidence Score | {{ "%.2f" | format(finding.exposure.confidence_score) }} |
| Data Fields Exposed | {{ finding.exposure.data_fields | map(attribute='field_name') | join(', ') }} |
| Removal Tier | {{ finding.removal_tier }} ({% if finding.removal_tier == 1 %}automated{% elif finding.removal_tier == 2 %}email opt-out{% else %}manual{% endif %}) |
| Recommended Action | {{ finding.exposure.recommended_action }} |

**Exposed Fields Detail:**
{% for f in finding.exposure.data_fields %}
- `{{ f.field_name }}`: {{ f.match_type }} match (confidence: {{ "%.2f" | format(f.confidence) }})
{% endfor %}

{% if finding.reappearance_note %}
⚠️  **REAPPEARANCE:** {{ finding.reappearance_note }}

{% endif %}
---
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
*No broker exposures found in this scan.*

---
{% endif %}

## Brokers Checked — No Exposure Found

{% if brokers_clear %}
{{ brokers_clear | join(', ') }}
{% else %}
*All checked brokers returned findings, or no clear-broker data is available.*
{% endif %}

---

{% if breaches %}
## Breach Database Results

| Source | Breach Date | Fields Exposed |
|--------|-------------|----------------|
{% for breach in breaches %}
| {{ breach.source }} | {{ breach.breach_date }} | {{ breach.fields_exposed | join(', ') }} |
{% endfor %}

---

{% endif %}
## Recommended Actions

{% set ns = namespace(counter=1) %}
{% set immediate = brokers | selectattr('exposure.recommended_action', 'equalto', 'submit_removal') | list %}
{% set high = brokers | selectattr('exposure.recommended_action', 'equalto', 'confirm_and_submit') | list %}
{% set review = brokers | selectattr('exposure.recommended_action', 'equalto', 'manual_review') | list %}
{% set reverify = brokers | selectattr('exposure.recommended_action', 'equalto', 'reverify') | list %}

{% for finding in immediate %}
{{ ns.counter }}. **[IMMEDIATE]** Submit removal to {{ finding.name }} — {{ finding.exposure.data_fields | map(attribute='field_name') | join(', ') }}
{% set ns.counter = ns.counter + 1 %}
{% endfor %}
{% for finding in high %}
{{ ns.counter }}. **[HIGH]** Confirm and submit removal to {{ finding.name }} (confidence: {{ "%.2f" | format(finding.exposure.confidence_score) }})
{% set ns.counter = ns.counter + 1 %}
{% endfor %}
{% for finding in review %}
{{ ns.counter }}. **[REVIEW]** Manual review required at {{ finding.name }} — {{ finding.exposure.data_fields | map(attribute='field_name') | join(', ') }}
{% set ns.counter = ns.counter + 1 %}
{% endfor %}
{% for finding in reverify %}
{{ ns.counter }}. **[REVERIFY]** Re-verify current status at {{ finding.name }}
{% set ns.counter = ns.counter + 1 %}
{% endfor %}
{% if not brokers %}
*No actions required — no exposures found in this scan.*
{% endif %}

---

## Removal Status Summary

| Status | Count |
|--------|-------|
| Submitted | {{ removal_summary.submitted }} |
| Confirmed Removed | {{ removal_summary.confirmed }} |
| Pending Verification | {{ removal_summary.pending }} |
| Failed / Needs Retry | {{ removal_summary.failed }} |

---

*Report generated by TraceBurn {{ version }} — data stays local, no cloud sync*
